CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1969, pg. 2, reads: "Marches and closed sites. The controversial paramilitary Black Berets of Homewood complete with their police dogs, lead a portion of the Black Coalition toward construction sites in Oakland Monday... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Protest march against discrimination in construction jobs, passing Mellon Bank, Fifth Avenue, Oakland
